<paragraph blockId="106.[151,1437,150,1005]" box="[199,1004,295,321]" pageId="106" pageNumber="107">
<emphasis box="[199,255,295,320]" italics="true" pageId="106" pageNumber="107">Eggs</emphasis>
: Ov. F carried approximately 20– 
<specimenCount box="[635,720,295,321]" pageId="106" pageNumber="107" type="egg">30 eggs</specimenCount>
of 
