diameter.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="106.[151,1437,150,1005]" pageId="106" pageNumber="107">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,341,330,357]" pageId="106" pageNumber="107">Live colour.</emphasis>
Body green-orange, with red and orange spots and patches. P1 green, tip of fingers dark orangereddish. P2–4 light green-orange, with dark green-brownish bands.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="106.[151,1437,150,1005]" box="[199,614,402,429]" pageId="106" pageNumber="107">
